<p>Proposals submitted by the June 30&nbsp;deadline will have priority selection and are more likely to have stated preferences met.&nbsp;<span>Email Assistant&nbsp;Vice President for Research Melissa Emery Thompson (</span><a href=\"mailto:memery@unm.edu\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">memery@unm.edu</a><span>) with any questions.</span></p>

<p>The OVPR is excited to announce that Research &amp; Discovery Week 2025 will be hosted jointly by&nbsp;Central Campus and HSC&#39;s research offices. This year, organizers are introducing&nbsp;a new format that will bring the community together for a series of &quot;conference-style&quot; research events at the SUB&nbsp;and at locations on North Campus, to be determined.&nbsp;</p>
